Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the data flow in the Shams Personal Assistant system:

```plantuml
@startuml AhmedAbdelGawadFarag_Shams-Personal-Assistant

actor User
participant "Android App" as App
participant "BotManager" as BotManager
participant "DialogManager" as DialogManager
participant "RecordingManager" as RecordingManager
participant "Main Server" as MainServer
participant "NER Server" as NERServer
participant "Google Cloud\nSpeech-to-Text" as STT
participant "Google Cloud\nText-to-Speech" as TTS
participant "Intent Classifier" as IntentClassifier
participant "Action Providers" as Providers

User -> App: Speak command
App -> RecordingManager: Record audio
RecordingManager -> App: Audio file
App -> MainServer: Send audio file
MainServer -> STT: Convert speech to text
STT --> MainServer: Transcribed text
MainServer -> IntentClassifier: Classify intent
IntentClassifier --> MainServer: Identified intent
MainServer -> NERServer: Extract entities
NERServer --> MainServer: Extracted entities
MainServer -> Providers: Execute action
Providers --> MainServer: Action result
MainServer -> TTS: Convert response to speech
TTS --> MainServer: Audio response
MainServer --> App: Send response
App -> BotManager: Process response
BotManager -> DialogManager: Update dialog state
DialogManager --> BotManager: Updated state
BotManager --> App: Display response
App -> User: Play audio/Show text

@enduml
```